ated like a servant or an object for breeding. This quiet, poetic film directed by Jan Troell and based on the novel by Lillian Bos Ross is an overlooked classic that deserves a revisit! Also starring: Susan Tyrrell, Eileen Heckart, and Sam Bottoms</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">Screening at 2:45 pm</span></p>	{}	www.harrydeanstantonfest.org		https://www.facebook.com/events/2371527982939466/?notif_t=plan_user_joined&notif_id=1560961470129539		http://bit.ly/2D0GehX	{}	t	2019-06-19 16:57:34.535+00	2019-11-21 13:28:51.973+00	\N
