her assemblage elements, Kim aims to create a more immersive and unified visual and spatial experience that will grapple with concepts of time, perception, and memory.</span></p>	{}			https://www.facebook.com/events/1252917478198197/		http://bit.ly/2pIQ0SQ	{}	t	2019-03-20 01:29:55.939+00	2019-11-21 13:26:36.489+00	\N
