tle viewers as well. </span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">*Make it viewable from the road! The goal is that cars passing will be able to see it WITHOUT having to leave their car. </span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">*Use what you already have! No need to make unnecessary trips to the store! Get creative! </span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">*Have fun! </span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">***I will be adding a Google form to anonymously collect participating addresses beginning April 26th. PLEASE DON'T COMMIT TO ADDING YOUR ADDRESS IF YOU AREN'T GOING TO PROVIDE AN ART/ CREATIVE DISPLAY. In the meantime BRAINSTORM an epic idea! </span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">Want to help out? </span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">Any other questions/ ideas/ marketing strategies can be sent to Sarah at frontyardartshowlex@gmail.com </span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">Woot woot!!</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">Can’t wait!!! </span></p>	{}			https://www.facebook.com/events/1322088354669098/		https://bit.ly/3aWEm8Z	{remote}	t	2020-04-09 14:59:36.834+00	2020-04-09 15:34:43.547+00	\N
