5, 255);">https://www.wuky.org/importance-being-ernest-airs-wuky#stream/0</a></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">Social distancing and closed venues are no match for the wit and whimsy of Oscar Wilde, whose classic comedy THE IMPORTANCE OF BEING EARNEST has endured for 125 years, and will more than survive our current pandemic!</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">The play follows Algernon and Jack, two respectable London gentlemen, who use every trick in the book (except the truth) to outwit the other and find true love with their respective paramours, Cecily and Gwendolen.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">THE IMPORTANCE OF BEING EARNEST, by Oscar Wilde, was directed by </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/trent.stephens" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Trent Stephens</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">, adapted by </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100019278736857" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Kevin Lane Dearinger</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">, and produced for radio by </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/samuel.lockridge.3" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Samuel Lockridge</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">The play features Mark Mozingo as Algernon, Paul Thomas as Lane and Merriman, </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/samuel.lockridge.3" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Samuel Lockridge</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);"> as Jack, Janet Scott as Lady Bracknell, </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/rachael.magill" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Raylee Magill</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);"> as Gwendolen, </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/amelia.saratoga.collins" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Amelia Collins</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);"> as Cecily, Catherine Pleis Gaffney as Miss Prism, and </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/shayne.brakefield" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Shayne Brakefield</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);"> as Canon Chausible. </span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">THE IMPORTANCE OF BEING EARNEST was originally sponsored by Melissa Lebus Watt and </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/debrahensleyinsurance/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Debra Hensley - State Farm Insurance Agent</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">, and </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Community-Trust-Bank/155939121137506" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Community Trust Bank</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">, with additional support from </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/LexArts/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LexArts</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);"> and </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/NAIIsaacKY/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(56, 88, 152); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">NAI Isaac</a><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41);">.</span></p>	{}	https://www.wuky.org/importance-being-ernest-airs-wuky#stream/0		https://www.facebook.com/events/279149909928722/		https://bit.ly/2B3zbat	{remot