quipment or tech savvy to</p><p class="ql-indent-1">engage.</p><p class="ql-indent-1"><br></p><p>Finally, for the first time the esteemed panel of judges as well as audiences will be able to</p><p>participate as though we're all here in Lexington sans commute (or the need for parking).</p><p><br></p><p>#JumpInTheTank</p>	{}	https://www.genglobal.org/index.php/united-states/fish-tank-emerging-entrepreneurs-arts-1	https://www.eventbrite.com/e/fish-tank-emerging-entrepreneurs-in-the-arts-tickets-115588940633		https://www.eventbrite.com/e/fish-tank-emerging-entrepreneurs-in-the-arts-tickets-115588940633	https://bit.ly/35KsENJ	{}	t	2020-10-24 17:32:23.406+00	2020-10-24 19:51:18.845+00	\N
