atus production.</em></p>	{}	https://finearts.uky.edu/theatre-dance/events/watsons-laura-wade-0			https://www.eventbrite.com/e/the-watsons-by-laura-wade-tickets-142101957781	https://bit.ly/3cIXWrB	{theater,remote}	t	2021-03-17 22:27:17.451+00	2021-04-13 15:34:48.316+00	\N
